<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for the Silenced</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Feb 09, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Am I so wise <br></br>
that I have nothing <br></br>
left to learn, <br></br>
or just afraid of <br></br>
what I might hear?
</p>

 <p>
Though others cannot, <br></br>
the voice of God still speaks, <br></br>
warning that justice comes, <br></br>
both for me <br></br>
and for those <br></br>
I have silenced.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


